channel.title: Client Error Message -- error_game_js5connect
channel.description:
Hello, I run Life-Scape on a seperate computer in my house, I am on a differnet computer to make sure my client works.
I download and run the client, its seems to work fine, but then I recieve this error message -- error_game_js5connect.
How can I fix it?
Never mind, I fixed the issue. Sorry for taking your time.
